{"tid":2036993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人完全訓唔著","createTime":"2020-05-26T19:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T19:34:47.000Z","uid":227271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03e8b0a4a7af933fd5c00798d27ce2d952ae36ca","tid":2036993,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"一恰埋眼就諗起班藍絲廢老聽日個得戚樣<br />\n<br />\n一諗到佢地個嘴臉就嬲到訓唔著<br />\n<br />\n成班賤種淨係識趨炎附勢依附權貴<br />\n<br />\n永遠唔識思考<br />\n<br />\n同佢地用歷史同Logic辯論永遠都無用<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地大多都唔識歷史<br />\n<br />\n講邏輯又聽唔明，但又駁唔到<br />\n<br />\n跟住就連番毫無邏輯可言兼扭曲真實既歪理<br />\n<br />\n再話你讀書讀壞腦<br />\n<br />\n「要不是黨照顧香港，你們早就（下刪十萬字）」<br />\n<br />\n喂呀哥！香港開阜個時中國共產黨係邊？<br />\n<br />\n香港經濟起飛黃金年代個時中國又搞緊咩？<br />\n<br />\n零三年大陸人黎消費救返香港？我呸！<br />\n<br />\n唔係你送沙士單野會搞成咁？<br />\n<br />\n成件事就好似唔小心係樓上跌左舊磚頭落黎<br />\n<br />\n但無叫樓下既你避開，到舊磚撞到你頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n就走返落黎搵塊紗布幫你止血，再同你講我係咪好好人呢<br />\n<br />\n點知塊妙布有菌既，幫你止左血，但你細菌入血<br />\n<br />\n你睇下自由行落到黎香港變成點？<br />\n<br />\n仲未計每日唔止150個支國人，相信各位都有眼見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到依家國安法<br />\n<br />\n「你唔搞事咪無人拉你」<br />\n<br />\n請問幫支國大頭奶粉事件既受害人爭取既人係咪搞事？<br />\n<br />\n早排提早公布疫情既支國醫生有無搞事？<br />\n<br />\n等等等等事件都話你到你聽啦？<br />\n<br />\n你班藍絲廢老又盲又聾架？定個腦塞左呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得維持現況就得，叫人唔好搞亂<br />\n<br />\n唔好阻人搵錢買樓供樓<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦你<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知點解仲未買到樓<br />\n<br />\n買到仲要供十幾二十甚至三十年？仲唔多謝黨？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嬲到我，根本訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一齊開佢老母拖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人唔係好恰</span></span>"},{"pid":"92cb4ae85df5494773b86e3fbfd550632869b6d0","tid":2036993,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:27:39.000Z","msg":"番緊工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLyoNQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLyoNQP.png&h=a8149769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f855334e91dbdd86e17e388a9223162dc290373","tid":2036993,"uid":227271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:30:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔係叫大家一定要出</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只係唔可以咩都唔做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算屋企用下Twitter 都好，總有野係你做到"},{"pid":"ff76d0f5bc8f33427ef3f69cc1842100d72bf8ce","tid":2036993,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92cb4ae85df5494773b86e3fbfd550632869b6d0","tid":2036993,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:27:39.000Z","msg":"番緊工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLyoNQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLyoNQP.png&h=a8149769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:31:08.000Z","msg":"辛苦你咁夜仲開工"},{"pid":"ff1decad7295f34b84214105f9534089bbcebb48","tid":2036993,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff76d0f5bc8f33427ef3f69cc1842100d72bf8ce","tid":2036993,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92cb4ae85df5494773b86e3fbfd550632869b6d0","tid":2036993,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T19:27:39.000Z","msg":"番緊工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLyoNQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLyoNQP.png&h=a8149769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/187080